 TEST 008 TS — Flag-selective persistence
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
 Purpose:
   Prove KeeperRecord routes to jText file and DatabaseEntry routes to
   SQLite while the other 9800 events stay in-memory only on the persist path.
   Expect higher ops/sec than persisting all 10000 events.

 Plan: 10000 in-memory events
   • indices 0..99     → KeeperRecord  (jText file)
   • indices 100..199 → DatabaseEntry (SQLite)
   • remainder           → no persist flags

